---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Wojciech Trocki — API platforms, developer tools, and AI at MongoDB.">
  <section style="max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem 6rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #f1f5f9;">About</h1>

    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; align-items: center;">
      <img src="/assets/profile.png" alt="Wojciech Trocki" style="width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; border: 3px solid #334155; flex-shrink: 0;" />
      <div>
        <h2 style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; color: #e2e8f0;">Wojciech Trocki</h2>
        <p style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9375rem;">Engineer, API Platform at <strong style="color: #34d399;">MongoDB</strong></p>
        <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 0.875rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Poznań, Poland &middot; Building platforms for developers worldwide</p>
        <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 0.875rem;">Pronounced "Voytek"</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="border-top: 1px solid #1e293b; padding-top: 2rem;">
      <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        I'm a platform engineer specializing in API infrastructure, authentication, and developer tooling. At MongoDB I work on the API Platform team building identity and access layers for cloud services — including authentication for programmatic access and AI agents, traffic shaping middleware, and API governance.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Previously a Principal Engineer at Red Hat Cloud Services, where I led a mobile backend team building SDKs, GraphQL backends, and SSO integrations that federated enterprise identity into cloud services. I'm an active API Champion, AsyncAPI contributor, and open-source maintainer.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        I build AI-augmented engineering tools — MCP servers, Claude Code skills, and developer workflows that make engineers more productive. I actively speak at and attend industry events.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="border-top: 1px solid #1e293b; padding-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h3 style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.0625rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; color: #e2e8f0;">Areas of Expertise</h3>

      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">

        <div style="background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border: 1px solid rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.15); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;">
          <span style="background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.12); color: #34d399; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 9999px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">AI-Augmented Engineering</span>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6;">
            Build AI-augmented developer workflows — MCP servers, coding agent skills, and code generation tooling. Maintain open-source AI tools. Speak at industry conferences on the next generation of AI-assisted engineering.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.15); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;">
          <span style="background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.12); color: #f472b6; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 9999px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">API Specs &amp; Standards</span>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6;">
            Drive spec-first API design with OpenAPI and GraphQL. Lead schema governance, automated linting pipelines, and API design reviews. Contribute to the AsyncAPI specification. Build AI-assisted tooling for API review and code generation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;">
          <span style="background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.12); color: #34d399; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 9999px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">API-Driven Tooling</span>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6;">
            Build SDKs, Terraform providers, and code generation pipelines from OpenAPI specs. Own API client tooling — templates, validation, and automated release workflows. Enable developers to consume APIs in the languages and tools they already use.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="position: relative; background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.3); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); border-radius: 0.75rem; overflow: hidden;">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 0.75rem;">
            <div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-left: 8px solid transparent; border-right: 8px solid transparent; border-bottom: 12px solid #3b82f6; flex-shrink: 0;"></div>
            <span style="background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15); color: #60a5fa; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 9999px;">API Middleware</span>
          </div>

          <div style="margin: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; border-left: 2px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;">
            <div style="position: relative;">
              <div style="position: absolute; left: -1.65rem; top: 0.8rem; width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #3b82f6;"></div>
              <span style="background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15); color: #818cf8; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 9999px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Authentication &amp; Identity</span>
              <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6;">
                Build OAuth 2.0 machine-to-machine authentication for programmatic access and AI agents. Author threat models for token management and identity federation. Orchestrate auth frameworks across SSO, MFA, and social login.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="position: relative;">
              <div style="position: absolute; left: -1.65rem; top: 0.8rem; width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #3b82f6;"></div>
              <span style="background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15); color: #fbbf24; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 9999px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Traffic Shaping</span>
              <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6;">
                Design traffic shaping middleware protecting API infrastructure at scale. Implement token bucket algorithms with distributed state, circuit breaking, and policy-driven throttling. Establish latency SLOs and drive reliability programs.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="position: relative;">
              <div style="position: absolute; left: -1.65rem; top: 0.8rem; width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #3b82f6;"></div>
              <span style="background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12); color: #60a5fa; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 9999px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">API Lifecycle &amp; Versioning</span>
              <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6;">
                Design API versioning strategies and deprecation policies. Manage the full API lifecycle from design review through GA to sunset — balancing stability with evolution.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="position: relative;">
              <div style="position: absolute; left: -1.65rem; top: 0.8rem; width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #3b82f6;"></div>
              <span style="background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.12); color: #34d399; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 9999px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Analytics &amp; Governance</span>
              <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6;">
                Instrument API usage analytics, telemetry, and observability pipelines. Drive API governance through design standards, automated linting, and review workflows that scale across engineering orgs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;">
          <span style="background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12); color: #a5b4fc; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 9999px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Cloud Native Infrastructure</span>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6;">
            Operate polyglot platform infrastructure (Go, Node.js, Java) at scale — container orchestration, service mesh, monitoring and metrics pipelines, and performance optimization. Drive reliability programs with SLOs and operational best practices.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="border-top: 1px solid #1e293b; padding-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h3 style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.0625rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #e2e8f0;">Engineering Principles</h3>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;">
        <h4 style="font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0;">Structure over Detail</h4>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;">Design docs define scope, interfaces, and risk — not implementation minutiae. Think in contracts and boundaries to unblock parallel delivery at AI-native speed.</p>
        <h4 style="font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0;">Enable Others</h4>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;">Drive architecture and bridges that unblock adjacent teams. Invest in shared patterns, specs, and tooling so the next person moves faster.</p>
        <h4 style="font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0;">Design for Security, Durability, Operational Excellence &amp; Performance</h4>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;">Treat these as first-class features, not afterthoughts. Assess early, plan ahead, bake them into architecture decisions from the start.</p>
        <h4 style="font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0;">Ownership</h4>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0;">Own what you build — decisions, outcomes, and mess. Push back on process that slows delivery without adding clarity or safety.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="border-top: 1px solid #1e293b; padding-top: 2rem;">
      <h3 style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.0625rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #e2e8f0;">Elsewhere</h3>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem;">
        <a href="https://github.com/wtrocki" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; color: #cbd5e1; background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/wojciech-t-39574526" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; color: #cbd5e1; background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/typeapi" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; color: #cbd5e1; background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;">X / Twitter</a>
        <a href="https://dev.to/wtrocki" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; color: #cbd5e1; background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;">Dev.to</a>
        <a href="https://medium.com/@wtr" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; color: #cbd5e1; background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;">Medium</a>
        <a href="mailto:wojciech@wtrocki.com" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; color: #cbd5e1; background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;">Email</a>
        <a href="https://leaddev.com/community/wojtek-trocki" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; color: #cbd5e1; background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;">LeadDev</a>
        <a href="https://patents.google.com/?q=(Wojciech)&amp;inventor=Trocki&amp;oq=Wojciech+Trocki" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; color: #cbd5e1; background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;">Patents</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
